summary: The kid has most likely been alone a big part of his life, but if there is one thing that is always there, it’s the world....
caption:
The kid has most likely been alone a big part of his life, but if there is one thing that is always there, it’s the world. However changing it may be, the sea is still the sea and the sky is still the sky. And if you ever need to talk to someone, talk to your friend, real or not, or play a tune. You don’t have to be alone when you have the whole world as company.

Here’s a video of sort that we’ve made. It’s actually the first time I’ve made one so any tips or advice about software would be much appreciated. Feedback is also nice.

As for the video itself, the clips are clearly from Moominvalley(1019) and the song is [ Vagabond by MisterWives ]. It’s a nice song that’s been in our head, so hopefully you’ll like it as well. And if you want to make a better version of it; go ahead, I’ll be looking forward to seeing what you lovely humans can do.

Also, regarding the episode from Moomin(1990) in which Snufkin watches Moomin sleep, I’m working on a transcript/summary for it. That way all who speak English can understand the episode and enjoy it as well. What do you all think of that? Trust me, it’s quite a fun episode. 

Oh yeah, should probably mention, you can call me Wallery Wallin if you’d like.

summary: After finally watching an episode of Moominvalley, this is what I got
body:
After finally watching an episode of Moominvalley, this is what I got

(I didn’t watch the first episode. I watched the one where snufkin electrocutes a guy, steals children, and ends up in prison)

  • Moomin- oblivious gay
  • Snufkin periodically abandons his friends
  • Little my is actually a child. For a while after browsing tumblr I thought she was older than them
  • Snufkin is an anarchist
  • Park keeper is a dick
  • Police grandmothers are wholesome
  • Little My is an absolute gremlin
  • Like, what is she planning?
  • I feel like eventually she’s gonna murder them
  • Moomin is moomin /troll/?
  • Moomin is FLUFFY
  • All in all an adorable show
  • Very good energy to it

summary: I've had a few ppl ask (mostly on Twitter) why I claim Snufkin as Sámi well...
body:
I’ve had a few ppl ask (mostly on Twitter) why I claim Snufkin as Sámi well…

• Wanderlust- All Sámi people I’ve met, myself included have intense wanderlust and aspirations of a nomadic life. This is what our ancestors did and what some of us still do to this day.

• Eco Anarchist- Hell yeah, lots of us are incredibly anti-government, anti-capitalist, and pro-environment.

• Music- Snufkin is shown knowing multiple instruments and being raised Sámi (at least in my case) meant it was expected to being able to play instruments.

• Minimalist- Snufkin carries his whole life around with him making it easy to move around but says attached to one specific place. That just has Sámi vibes.

• Origin- The Moomins were made in Finland and have many strong bases of Finnish culture and lore like Finnish trolls. So it is very likely Tove based Snufkin off of Sámi people (and yes there are some Sámi stereotypes in the old books relating to Snufkin but at least Snufkin is shown to be his own character.)

• Because I said so- We really don’t get representation ever in mainstream media and when we do, it just circles on stereotypes *ahem Kristoff* so it is nice for us to see ourselves in a character.
